      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773731449813,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "> In this learning procedure, the algo compares the new\n   problem instances with instances already seen in the \n   training, which have been stored in memory for reference\n   rather than performing explicit generalization.\n> eg , KNN, SVM, PCA, Radial Basis Function(RBF)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "> In this learning procedure, the algo compares the new\n   problem instances with instances already seen in the \n   training, which have been stored in memory for reference\n   rather than performing explicit generalization.\n> eg , KNN, SVM, PCA, Radial Basis Function(RBF)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
